snippet.title: Celebrities DEFENDING Johnny Depp against Amber Heard  | OG CELEBRITY
snippet.description:
The Johnny Depp and Amber Heard court case is still raging on and more information is reaching the news daily! This has also dragged a lot of other celebrities into the case and most of them are taking sides. The vast majority are taking the side of Johnny Depp against Amber Heard. Some of the biggest celebrities who have publicly defended Johnny Depp are Jason Momoa, Elon Musk, Sia and Alice Cooper!
